Combines two CRC checksums into one\&. For two binaries or iolists, \fIData1\fR\& and \fIData2\fR\& with sizes of \fISize1\fR\& and \fISize2\fR\&, with CRC checksums \fICRC1\fR\& and \fICRC2\fR\&\&.
